folder: Myrtle Avenue & Stanhope Street, Brooklyn, NY
text:
Myrtle Ave., at the S.W. corner of Stanhope Street, also showing rear of buildings facing on Himrod Street. The house at right behind the pillar, is at 140 Stanhope Street. Overhead is the Myrtle Ave. Elevated Line of
the B.M.T.
May 1929.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.

folder: Stanhope Street & Myrtle Avenue, Brooklyn, NY
